## ğŸƒ Running Tests

### Run all tests
```bash
./gradlew test
```

### Run with specific browser
```bash
./gradlew test -Pbrowser=chromium
./gradlew test -Pbrowser=firefox
./gradlew test -Pbrowser=webkit
```

### Run in headless mode
```bash
./gradlew test -Pheadless=true
```

### Run with specific environment
```bash
./gradlew test -Penv=dev
./gradlew test -Penv=qa
./gradlew test -Penv=prod
```

### Run smoke tests
```bash
./gradlew smokeTest
```

### Run regression tests with parallel execution
```bash
./gradlew regressionTest -Pparallel=true -PthreadCount=3
```

